The vampire Angelus, now known as Angel, has a human soul,
but committed terrible crimes in the past. Seeking forgiveness
and trying to redeem himself, he moves from Sunnydale (and a
relationship with Buffy Summers, of "Buffy the Vampire Slayer")
to Los Angeles, where he helps the downtrodden by thwarting
the supernatural creatures that prey on them.
